== 监禁与处决 (1848–1852) ==
[[File:Nāser_al-Dīn_Schah.jpg|thumb]]]]
在巴达什特会议后，塔荷蕾和库杜斯一起前往[[馬贊德蘭省|馬贊德蘭省]]，并在那里他们分开。在[[馬贊德蘭省|馬贊德蘭省]]他们收到了侵扰，关于受到侵扰的原因，存在不同的记录。有记录认为是因为他们在同一个旅馆停留，并使用同一个公共浴室，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5A90fE_96ToC&lpg=PP1&dq=inauthor%3A%22Mangol%20Bayat%22&pg=PA117#v=onepage&q=sight%20lodging%20together%20inns%20public%20bath&f=false |title=Mysticism and Dissent: Sociorelgious Thought in Qajar Iran, Mangol Bayat, p. 118 |access-date=2018-01-04 |archive-date=2019-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730205849/https://books.google.com/books?id=5A90fE_96ToC&lpg=PP1&dq=inauthor%3A%22Mangol%20Bayat%22&pg=PA117#v=onepage&q=sight%20lodging%20together%20inns%20public%20bath&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>另一种记录认为，侵扰他们的是反巴比运动人士。<ref name="Women and the Family in Iran"/>在他们到达巴尔福鲁什后，他们受到了一些巴比教信徒的保护。

